35
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:25,880
and keeping me safe.

36
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,120
So...

37
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:30,760
So...

38
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:33,680
Who on earth are you?

39
