46
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,160
You and my mom...

47
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,000
You've never...

48
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,680
Heng,

49
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,240
in those years,

50
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:06,960
unable to bear Demon Lord Chi 's torture anymore,

51
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,240
