00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:31,920
Dad.

98
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:34,040
Dad.

99
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,320
Dad.

100
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:37,960
Dad.

101
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:49,560
Where are you from, little fox?

102
00:09:49,880 --> 00:09:50,880
Where are you from?

103
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:09,200
Jiu.

104
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,560
Your Highness?

105
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:22,600
Why did you become a common spiritual fox?

106
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:26,920
How about your magic arts?

107
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,160
Did you lose them?

108
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:44,280
I'm pregnant with His Majesty's baby.

109
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,400
What has happened?

110
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:05,960
You're fooled, Your Highness.

111
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:09,680
If you got pregnant

112
00:11:09,840 --> 00:11:11,320
from just kissing him,

113
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,920
I'd give birth to two sons.

114
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,360
Come on.

115
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,880
Now that you're here, just stay.

116
00:11:20,480 --> 00:11:21,320
Write down

117
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,600
everything about how you become

118
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,680
what you are.

119
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,240
Write it down.

120
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:49,360
Dad.

121
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:01,280
Your Majesty, thank you for saving me.

122
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:03,880
The poison hasn't been removed completely.

123
00:12:04,480 --> 00:12:05,920
You still need a good rest.

124
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:16,640
Min Su.

125
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,840
Your Majesty, how is Min Su doing?

126
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,040
He'll survive.

127
00:12:21,280 --> 00:12:21,760
Your Majesty,

128
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,600
can I beg you for something?

129
00:12:25,280 --> 00:12:26,040
My elder brother

130
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,880
Xu Yang

131
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:31,160
wouldn't spare Min Su.

132
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,200
Your Majesty,

133
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,400
can you help us?

134
00:12:39,040 --> 00:12:39,680
The two of you...

135
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:42,400
We've known each other since childhood.

136
00:12:43,720 --> 00:12:44,440
When I was young,

137
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:47,360
my brother wouldn't let me talk to anyone else.

138
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:50,120
Only Min Su stayed with me

139
00:12:50,680 --> 00:12:51,800
and took care of me.

140
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:57,000
I don't want to marry the guy chosen by my brother.

141
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:04,840
But he...

142
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,000
Your Majesty,

143
00:13:06,680 --> 00:13:07,800
I'll marry nobody

144
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,920
but Min Su.

145
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:13,760
I hope you can help me.

146
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:32,120
Your Majesty, you've underestimated me.

147
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,280
How could you trap me in such a small ward?

148
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:38,840
Demon Lord,

149
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:39,760
Her Highness is back.

150
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:41,240
Where is she?

151
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:42,240
Just outside the palace.

152
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,360
She's with Emperor Dong Hua.

153
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,200
Dong Hua?

154
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:05,800
Dong Hua,

155
00:14:06,240 --> 00:14:07,240
why is my sister injured?

156
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,360
She's poisoned with Qiushui Cold Toxin.

157
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,840
Qiushui?

158
00:14:15,040 --> 00:14:16,440
Dong Hua,

159
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:17,920
you saved her life.

160
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:20,440
We're deeply grateful.

161
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:27,200
The poison hasn't been removed completely.

162
00:14:27,610 --> 00:14:29,080
She still needs a good rest.

163
00:14:29,560 --> 00:14:30,960
Thank you for your advice.

164
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:40,720
Dong Hua,

165
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:43,000
can you tell me

166
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:47,080
what on earth has happened between
you and Heng on Baishui Mountain?

167
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:48,720
Nothing special.

168
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:49,920
I just met her by chance.

169
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,120
By chance?

170
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:56,080
Dong Hua, do you still remember

171
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:59,240
what you promised us at the Forbidden Land?

172
00:15:00,160 --> 00:15:00,600
Go ahead.

173
00:15:01,520 --> 00:15:03,040
I hope

174
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:06,440
you can marry Ji Heng.

175
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:11,640
I'm afraid I can't.

176
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,480
You made a promise.

177
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:14,840
Do you want to go back on it?

178
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,640
It has nothing to do with my promise.

179
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,720
It's just I've never planned

180
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,800
to get married.

181
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:23,000
You once promised

182
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,640
you'd say yes to my request

183
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,120
as long as it's not morally wrong

184
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:27,360
and it doesn't hurt anyone.

185
00:15:28,160 --> 00:15:30,000
Why are you making excuses?

186
00:15:33,280 --> 00:15:34,760
So what?

187
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:37,360
Dong Hua,

188
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:40,800
your marriage matters a lot.

189
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:43,320
It's not something just between you and me.

190
00:15:44,300 --> 00:15:47,200
I actually put it forward for the sake of the gods, the demons

191
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:49,680
and even the whole world.

192
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:53,720
The gods and the demons will live together in peace

193
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:54,960
and there won't be wars anymore.

194
00:15:55,160 --> 00:15:56,440
Isn't lasting peace

195
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:59,480
what you wish for?

196
00:16:08,200 --> 00:16:10,000
So, you want your sister to marry me

197
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:12,720
for lasting peace of the six worlds.

198
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:14,240
Exactly.

199
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:17,560
What else do you think?

200
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,000
In this case,

201
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:20,280
you can send Ji Heng

202
00:16:21,160 --> 00:16:23,760
to Tai Chen Palace in three months.

203
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,520
You agreed?

204
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:27,560
You have lofty ideals,

205
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:30,000
but you should also remember

206
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,320
Ji Heng will be one of the gods

207
00:16:31,680 --> 00:16:33,480
after she marries into our clan

208
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:35,160
and then won't have to follow the rules of the demons.

209
00:16:35,720 --> 00:16:36,120
Besides,

210
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:41,000
in case anything happens to your clan in the future,

211
00:16:41,920 --> 00:16:45,120
I'm sure you'll keep sparing no effort

212
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:47,600
for the peace of the universe

213
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:50,840
and won't leave your clan members acting against the law.

214
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:53,320
For this purpose,

215
00:16:53,960 --> 00:16:56,160
I have to fulfill your wish.

216
00:16:59,520 --> 00:17:01,400
You have a great deal of foresight.

217
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:03,600
I admire you.

218
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:09,160
I've said yes to your request.

219
00:17:09,680 --> 00:17:11,830
As for Ji Heng's guard,

220
00:17:12,880 --> 00:17:14,110
how about forgiving him?

221
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:16,160
Now that she's going to marry you,

222
00:17:16,830 --> 00:17:18,350
I'll spare him.

223
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,560
His Majesty often makes an inspection tour like this.

224
00:17:38,880 --> 00:17:40,240
It's not been a long time since he left.

225
00:17:40,600 --> 00:17:41,640
Why do you miss him so much?

226
00:17:42,480 --> 00:17:43,840
I'm really worried about you.

227
00:17:48,660 --> 00:17:51,600
His Majesty couldn't stay with you every day.

228
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:57,720
Well. Don't cry.

229
00:17:57,840 --> 00:17:59,560
His Majesty asked me to take good care of you.

230
00:18:02,950 --> 00:18:03,600
How about this?

231
00:18:04,130 --> 00:18:05,320
I'll open the ward

232
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:06,960
so that you can play around in the palace.

233
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:07,720
Okay?

234
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:15,080
Little fox, how can you lie to me?

235
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:22,720
I want to stay with His Majesty every now and then.

236
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:24,200
I'm going to meet him!

237
00:18:47,100 --> 00:18:48,080
You little fox.

238
00:18:48,680 --> 00:18:50,160
You deceived him into opening the ward.

239
00:18:52,810 --> 00:18:53,380
Your Majesty.

240
00:18:53,640 --> 00:18:54,920
Foster brother, you're back.

241
00:18:56,840 --> 00:18:57,440
Your Majesty.

242
00:18:59,150 --> 00:18:59,610
Your Majesty,

243
00:18:59,610 --> 00:19:01,040
it turns out the little fox went to meet you.

244
00:19:19,160 --> 00:19:20,840
Aren't they resin of cinnamomum camphora

245
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:21,640
and stamens of green lotuses from Baishui Mountain?

246
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,120
It turns out he went to collect medicine for me.

247
00:19:26,080 --> 00:19:26,880
These are the two kinds of effective medicine

248
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:28,920
to cure wounds, right?

249
00:19:36,080 --> 00:19:37,440
Get the gallipot here.

250
00:19:58,320 --> 00:19:59,880
His hand is injured.

251
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:01,600
It must've happened

252
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:03,120
when he got medicine for me.

253
00:20:05,040 --> 00:20:06,080
I'll also make

254
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:07,440
a great healing ointment for him.

255
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:10,000
Jiu from the Imperial Kitchen is good at cooking.

256
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,760
Ask her to prepare food for the fox.

257
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:15,040
There is one thing I have to report to you.

258
00:20:15,480 --> 00:20:16,800
Jiu disappeared.

259
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:19,480
I think she has something to do with the demon

260
00:20:19,640 --> 00:20:21,720
who came here disguised as you.

261
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:23,840
You liar.

262
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,280
I'm open and aboveboard.

263
00:20:25,560 --> 00:20:27,520
How could I be a spy of the demons?

264
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:29,080
I'm from Qingqiu.

265
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:30,880
You framed me up

266
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:33,160
just to stop me from coming back again.

267
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:35,160
Now that you care about the fox,

268
00:20:35,320 --> 00:20:37,680
how about letting my subordinate Yu Ru take care of it?

269
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:41,600
It's better to leave me alone.

270
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:42,600
I may live a longer life

271
00:20:42,760 --> 00:20:44,520
without your subordinate.

272
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:45,680
Don't bother.

273
00:20:46,320 --> 00:20:47,640
Now that there is no suitable person,

274
00:20:48,360 --> 00:20:49,680
I'll take care of it myself.

275
00:20:50,320 --> 00:20:50,840
Foster brother,

276
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,560
we know nothing about the little fox's background.

277
00:20:52,840 --> 00:20:55,040
I'm afraid it is transformed by some demon with magic arts.

278
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:56,560
You have to be careful.

279
00:20:57,000 --> 00:20:57,800
You're thinking too much.

280
00:21:29,080 --> 00:21:30,040
You can even cry.

281
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:31,760
Why can't you jump on me?

282
00:21:53,280 --> 00:21:55,200
He sent me a piece of jade.

283
00:21:56,200 --> 00:21:58,720
Is it the so-called token of affection?

284
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:03,520
You're so lively.

285
00:22:04,160 --> 00:22:05,800
I'm sorry that you got trapped in the soul-locking jade

286
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:07,640
and almost lost your life.

287
00:22:09,280 --> 00:22:10,280
It's nothing.

288
00:22:10,880 --> 00:22:12,280
I'm willing to do anything

289
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:13,920
as long as I can stay by your side.

290
00:22:24,120 --> 00:22:26,320
He used to be one of my generals.

291
00:22:27,120 --> 00:22:28,080
He was bold and powerful at that time

