293
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:34,320
Today,

294
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:39,760
I could do nothing but watch him die.

295
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:42,920
OMG.

296
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:45,040
I thought

297
00:22:45,700 --> 00:22:48,720
he's the most resolute and ruthless god
in the Four Seas and Eight Deserts,

298
00:22:49,320 --> 00:22:51,240
but he also feels sad sometimes.

299
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:56,920
What's so special

300
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,840
about love?

301
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:02,800
Why did a brave general like him choose to do that?

302
00:23:06,280 --> 00:23:07,680
He could've survived.

303
00:23:08,560 --> 00:23:09,240
Your Majesty,

304
00:23:09,480 --> 00:23:11,320
I'm willing to do anything for you,

305
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:12,680
but,

306
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:15,120
I don't want to die for you.

307
00:23:16,440 --> 00:23:17,880
It's not that I'm not sincere enough,

308
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:19,000
It's just

309
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:21,600
I prefer to live with you.

310
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:23,720
I have a great yearning to stay with you,

311
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:25,160
so I can't die.

312
00:23:25,720 --> 00:23:26,960
I hate to part with you.

313
00:23:57,080 --> 00:23:57,640
Your Highness,

314
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,480
you made trouble again.

315
00:23:59,720 --> 00:24:01,560
Do you know your fur is...

316
00:24:05,840 --> 00:24:06,600
Did you draw it?

317
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:12,480
Flowers bloom and fade and turn into mud.

318
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:16,520
Safe and peaceful, we stay with each other forever.

319
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:18,040
Si Ming, you're impolite.

320
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:19,880
How can read my poem without my permission?

321
00:24:20,840 --> 00:24:23,520
Just so so. It's a tongue twister at most.

322
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:24,720
You bad guy.

323
00:24:25,520 --> 00:24:27,400
But I think

324
00:24:27,560 --> 00:24:29,480
this painting is not bad.

325
00:24:31,240 --> 00:24:32,800
Speaking of Technique of the Buddha's Seal Wheel,

326
00:24:33,080 --> 00:24:35,240
