327
00:24:36,640 --> 00:24:39,600
The first is Mo Yuan from the Kunlun Mountain.

328
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:42,640
The second is the Buddha from Sukhavati.

329
00:24:43,120 --> 00:24:46,600
The third is His Majesty.

330
00:24:46,760 --> 00:24:48,000
You're most fortunate

331
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,800
to have a chance to see it.

332
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:50,920
That's for sure.

333
00:24:51,360 --> 00:24:52,840
His Majesty is so powerful.

334
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,600
I'm bound to spread it

335
00:24:54,760 --> 00:24:55,640
and let more people

336
00:24:55,800 --> 00:24:57,200
know about the heroic epic.

337
00:24:59,560 --> 00:25:01,160
Si Ming, where is that thing?

338
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:09,400
This is what you want.

339
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:11,800
Don't open it completely.

340
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:13,880
Take out as much as you need.

341
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:32,640
What is it?

342
00:25:51,960 --> 00:25:53,120
Cotton rose ointment.

343
00:25:56,080 --> 00:25:56,800
Did you make it?

344
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:11,520
Wait a second.

345
00:26:18,560 --> 00:26:19,040
Here you are.

346
00:26:25,840 --> 00:26:28,560
♪ Falling flowers have a soft voice. ♪

347
00:26:29,240 --> 00:26:32,040
♪ The wind talks to the Bodhi tree. ♪

348
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:39,440
♪ Bright-eyed, she's giving a little smile. ♪

349
00:26:39,480 --> 00:26:40,040
Not bad.

350
00:26:40,560 --> 00:26:47,480
♪ When it comes to destiny, she couldn't help missing him. ♪

351
00:26:49,320 --> 00:26:50,080
Good girl.

352
00:26:54,600 --> 00:27:02,840
♪ Acacia sees time flying and the yearning between lovers. ♪

353
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:10,080
♪ She gets lovesick when failing to see him. ♪

354
00:27:10,520 --> 00:27:17,800
♪ Life is like a wordless book. ♪

355
00:27:17,960 --> 00:27:21,400
