00:28:17,840 --> 00:28:19,760
The mortals usually paint red the first petal

367
00:28:20,560 --> 00:28:22,040
on the "double nine" diagrams

368
00:28:22,600 --> 00:28:24,120
on the Winter Solstice.

369
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:26,080
By then,

370
00:28:27,120 --> 00:28:28,840
I'll get your paws red

371
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:30,040
and paint with them.

372
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:31,520
What do you think?

373
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:33,920
His Majesty is also thinking about the future.

374
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:36,640
We'll spend a lot of time with each other in the future.

375
00:28:42,600 --> 00:28:43,000
Alright.

376
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:44,400
From now on,

377
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:46,200
I'll stop eating my head off.

378
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:48,200
I'll be a useful fox

379
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:50,000
to bring glory to him.

380
00:28:54,320 --> 00:29:02,840
♪ They remember each other no matter how the world is changing. ♪

381
00:29:02,940 --> 00:29:10,320
♪ I'll never give up unless the earth and heaven get old. ♪

382
00:29:10,400 --> 00:29:17,400
♪ I hope destiny will bring us together. ♪

383
00:29:18,080 --> 00:29:21,280
♪ It's melancholy and sorrowful. ♪

384
00:29:21,520 --> 00:29:27,600
♪ It's miserable to part with who you love. ♪

385
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:32,960
I'll be a useful fox.

386
00:29:33,320 --> 00:29:35,800
Well. I'll try to do that when summer is over.

387
00:29:59,320 --> 00:30:01,080
You really love the little fox.

388
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:02,280
To let it enjoy the shade,

389
00:30:02,440 --> 00:30:03,600
you've got two sandalwood trees cut

390
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:05,120
and rock crystal has been used to avoid water.

391
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,240
In this way

392
00:30:06,280 --> 00:30:08,360
can it relax in the cool pavilion in midsummer.

393
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:15,000
I'm even inferior to a fox.

394
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:17,280
Your Highness, please don't say that.

395
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:18,880
It's just a pet.

396
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:22,320
I've done so many things

397
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:24,600
for the sake of him.

398
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,280
But in the end,

399
00:30:26,880 --> 00:30:28,480
it's a pet that has benefited from this.

400
00:30:47,760 --> 00:30:48,400
Your Majesty,

401
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:51,400
have you always been reading Buddhist scriptures alone

402
00:30:52,120 --> 00:30:53,800
in the daytime

403
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:56,440
and at night?

404
00:31:07,880 --> 00:31:08,800
As long as I'm here,

405
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,600
he won't feel lonely again.

406
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,560
I'll give all best things in the world

407
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,720
to him.

408
00:31:14,520 --> 00:31:16,280
When I'm able to speak,

409
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:19,000
I'll deceive him into going to Qingqiu.

410
00:31:19,480 --> 00:31:21,760
By then, I'll say this to him.

411
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:22,640
Look.

412
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:24,400
Stars here are so big.

413
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:25,420
They're not cute.

414
00:31:25,780 --> 00:31:27,940
I can take you to Qingqiu

415
00:31:27,940 --> 00:31:28,700
and watch stars there.

416
00:31:29,320 --> 00:31:29,800
Okay.

417
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:57,880
Has His Majesty seen you

418
00:31:57,960 --> 00:32:00,320
behave like this?

419
00:32:04,480 --> 00:32:06,920
You won't listen to me unless I mention His Majesty.

420
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,360
Are you angry?

421
00:32:17,040 --> 00:32:17,840
How about shaking hands?

422
00:32:23,320 --> 00:32:24,640
Anger makes you age more quickly.

423
00:32:26,040 --> 00:32:28,000
Look. I'm old enough.

424
00:32:28,280 --> 00:32:29,840
I can't remember anything.

425
00:32:32,200 --> 00:32:33,720
I can't remember who said

426
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:35,480
the root of Hanshi grass

427
00:32:35,720 --> 00:32:37,160
is effective in helping people forget sorrow

428
00:32:37,480 --> 00:32:39,880
and its flowers are top seasoning.

429
00:32:41,440 --> 00:32:43,600
And I can't remember who wants the seed.

430
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,760
It's you.

431
00:32:55,320 --> 00:32:58,200
I looked for it on purpose

432
00:32:58,280 --> 00:33:00,200
when I went to Sukhavati for the Buddha's lectures.

433
00:33:00,400 --> 00:33:02,420
It's said it's the last seed on Ling Mountain

434
00:33:02,420 --> 00:33:04,160
in the Four Seas and Eight Deserts.

435
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:05,480
The last one.

436
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:08,680
You're happy now.

437
00:33:10,480 --> 00:33:11,560
I'll give it to you

438
00:33:11,680 --> 00:33:12,400
when you leave the Sky Kingdom.

439
00:33:13,760 --> 00:33:14,840
Your scared me.

440
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:17,640
Don't eat it!

441
00:33:33,080 --> 00:33:34,400
I'll bury it here.

442
00:33:35,760 --> 00:33:37,560
The location won't matter

443
00:33:38,920 --> 00:33:40,240
if I can stay with His Majesty in the future.

444
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:53,920
It's just cooked.

445
00:33:56,320 --> 00:33:56,960
By me.

446
00:33:58,040 --> 00:33:58,600
Your Majesty.

447
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:01,840
I've been thinking about it.

448
00:34:01,840 --> 00:34:03,880
His Majesty and I don't share the same hobbies.

449
00:34:04,320 --> 00:34:06,120
I'm not good at anything he can do.

450
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:07,080
But unexpectedly,

451
00:34:07,080 --> 00:34:09,280
he's also good at cooking, the only thing I'm expert at.

452
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,600
I finally found something

453
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:17,670
we're both good at.

454
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,190
I'm much relieved.

455
00:34:36,040 --> 00:34:36,760
Is it good?

456
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:38,440
For real,

457
00:34:40,670 --> 00:34:42,280
it's so...

458
00:34:42,670 --> 00:34:45,230
...so awful.

459
00:34:48,560 --> 00:34:51,280
What should be the look on my face when I talk to him?

460
00:34:52,120 --> 00:34:53,400
My auntie once told me

461
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,670
a story about a bride.

462
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:57,360
She was not good at cooking.

463
00:34:57,840 --> 00:34:59,800
One day, she was seized by a whim

464
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:01,040
and decided to cook soup.

465
00:35:01,640 --> 00:35:04,040
She won high praise from her husband.

466
00:35:04,680 --> 00:35:07,800
Later, the bride tasted the soup

467
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,640
when she did the dishes,

468
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:11,320
only to find

469
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:13,800
her husband said those words

470
00:35:14,160 --> 00:35:15,520
to make her happy.

471
00:35:16,120 --> 00:35:17,040
So...

472
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:22,280
Then the couple loved each other more.

473
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:25,160
It became an interesting story

474
00:35:25,160 --> 00:35:26,200
on everybody's lips.

475
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:29,320
I can't tell him it's awful.

476
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:55,600
Your Majesty,

477
00:35:57,200 --> 00:35:58,920
please observe carefully

478
00:35:59,040 --> 00:36:02,000
and realize I'm smiling with a little reluctance.

479
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:03,120
It'd be best

480
00:36:04,240 --> 00:36:06,120
if you taste it yourself.

481
00:36:10,600 --> 00:36:11,600
Do you mean...

482
00:36:16,240 --> 00:36:17,400
You want to have some more?

483
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,200
There is no more for today.

484
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:22,080
I'll cook for you tomorrow.

485
00:36:26,680 --> 00:36:27,320
Don't bother.

486
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:29,480
I've tasted it.

487
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:31,920
It's awful.

488
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,680
But I think

489
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:36,040
it may be to your taste now that you're a different species.

490
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:38,040
So I took it to you.

491
00:36:38,800 --> 00:36:39,440
As expected,

492
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:43,040
you foxes really have a different taste.

493
00:37:44,600 --> 00:37:46,280
I've eaten so much food prepared by His Majesty

494
00:37:46,640 --> 00:37:48,040
that I've lost lots of fur.

495
00:37:49,560 --> 00:37:50,720
If it goes on like this,

496
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,360
I'd become bald.

497
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:57,200
It seems I have no other choice

498
00:37:57,440 --> 00:37:58,880
but to tell him the truth.

499
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:02,760
Alright.

500
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:05,040
I'll use body language to tell him

501
00:38:05,600 --> 00:38:08,040
I don't like the carp.

502
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:10,840
Good tea.

503
00:38:11,320 --> 00:38:12,000
There is a guest.

504
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:14,520
I can't eavesdrop on them.

505
00:38:15,040 --> 00:38:16,040
It's impolite.

506
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:18,720
Your Majesty,

507
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:20,800
I haven't heard that

508
00:38:20,920 --> 00:38:22,120
you're interested in pets.

509
00:38:22,240 --> 00:38:23,880
Why did you suddenly raise a spiritual fox?

510
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:25,000
It's special.

511
00:38:25,720 --> 00:38:27,680
Maybe it's destiny.

512
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:30,280
Don't try to fool me.

513
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:31,760
I've seen spiritual foxes

514
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:32,800
better-looking than that.

515
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,960
The ladies in the Bai family of Qingqiu

516
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:37,760
are all gorgeous.

517
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,440
What's special

518
00:38:39,560 --> 00:38:40,880
about your fox?

519
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:44,760
It likes the sweet and sour fish

520
00:38:45,080 --> 00:38:46,240
made by me.

521
00:38:53,600 --> 00:38:55,080
It's really special.

522
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:01,800
Such being the case,

523
00:39:02,640 --> 00:39:04,000
if I tell him

524
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:05,440
I was lying,

525
00:39:05,560 --> 00:39:05,960
then...

526
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:08,440
Anyway,

527
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:10,400
it's a white lie.

528
00:39:11,200 --> 00:39:12,960
I'd better just let it continue.

529
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,320
If I keep eating the fish cooked by him,

530
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:18,880
all my fur would fall out,

531
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:21,160
but it doesn't matter.

532
00:39:23,120 --> 00:39:24,240
I'll pretend

533
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:25,640
it's time to molt.

534
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,920
Did you just smile?

535
00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:00,040
Do you like it?

536
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:03,320
Yes.

537
00:40:20,160 --> 00:40:22,280
Have a look. Do you like it?

538
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:25,440
I like all your paintings.

539
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:39,760
Wait for me at the central yard if you wake up.

540
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:41,600
I'll feed you.

541
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:47,800
What's special about that little fox?

542
00:40:48,680 --> 00:40:49,680
It's more important than me in your mind.

543
00:40:50,840 --> 00:40:51,520
Why?

544
00:40:52,120 --> 00:40:52,680
Anyway,

545
00:40:53,240 --> 00:40:54,600
in this case, I can't go to the west desert

546
00:40:54,600 --> 00:40:55,960
to do what you want me to.

547
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:59,040
I promised your father I'd look after you.

548
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:00,600
I mean what I say.

549
00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:03,040
It's just a pet. Don't take it seriously.

550
00:41:24,720 --> 00:41:25,360
See?

551
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:27,120
In his mind,

552
00:41:27,240 --> 00:41:28,760
you're just a pet.

553
00:41:29,400 --> 00:41:31,040
But you always dream of staying with him.

554
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:33,000
Don't you think it's ridiculous?

555
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:37,640
Now I can go to the west desert and give rain.

556
00:41:38,320 --> 00:41:39,760
I wonder if he's still interested in you

557
00:41:40,480 --> 00:41:42,480
when I come back.

558
00:41:43,720 --> 00:41:46,680
I hope I can still see you in Tai Chen Palace.

559
00:42:17,280 --> 00:42:18,600
His Majesty is so nice to me.

560
00:42:20,040 --> 00:42:22,120
Am I really just a pet in his mind?

561
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:25,240
If he knows my true identity...

562
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:27,880
If I tell him

563
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:29,080
I'm Princess of Qingqiu,

564
00:42:30,360 --> 00:42:31,560
will he blame me?

565
00:42:33,320 --> 00:42:34,760
He drew paintings with me

566
00:42:35,720 --> 00:42:37,480
and sent me such nice white jade.

567
00:42:37,880 --> 00:42:39,720
He said so much to me with me in his arms.

568
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:24,320
Little thing,

569
00:43:24,800 --> 00:43:26,800
you're so naughty,

570
00:43:27,040 --> 00:43:28,760
but His Majesty just won't get mad at you.

571
00:43:29,960 --> 00:43:32,440
That's because I'm important in his mind.

572
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:41,200
Go with me.

573
00:43:41,520 --> 00:43:42,600
